    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A generously-appointed bathroom with a wide variety of smart features, such as a bath and shower which remember the user's preferences, a toilet capable of diet analysis and self-sanitation, a vanity mirror with integrated smart-screen and VI, linked to the local datapool and able to access the latest NC fashion trends (order with just one tap!) and more.</p><p>A bathroom is included in each room rented on the 4th floor of the Afterlife, and cannot be removed. Does not take an option slot.</p><p>Allows up to three Edgerunners to keep clean and fresh while staying in their HQ. When doing so, they receive +2 to Personal Grooming checks while staying there, which expires 2 in-game hours after leaving the Afterlife.</p>"
    },
